    <item>
      <title>Eclipse 使用月影面板将美国太阳能发电量削减 30 吉瓦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/eclipse-to-cut-us-solar-by-30-gigawatts-as-moon-shades-panels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周一的日全食期间，美国将损失超过 30 吉瓦的太阳能——大约相当于30个核反应堆的产量——因为在黄金发电时段阳光被阻挡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/eclipse-to-cut-us-solar-by-30-gigawatts-as-moon-shades-panels</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着电动超级跑车竞争的升温，法拉利开设细胞实验室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ferrari-opens-cell-lab-as-electric-supercar-competition-heats-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法拉利公司 (Ferrari NV) 推出了一个新的实验室来研究锂电池，准备在明年年底前生产首款全电动超级跑车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ferrari-opens-cell-lab-as-electric-supercar-competition-heats-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:59:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价上涨，俄罗斯第一季度收入大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/russia-s-revenue-jumps-in-first-quarter-amid-rising-oil-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯报告第一季度收入大幅增长，部分原因是一次性纳税和油价上涨，因为该国继续承受因乌克兰战争而受到的制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/russia-s-revenue-jumps-in-first-quarter-amid-rising-oil-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:57:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街吹捧欧洲为下一阶段股市上涨的赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/wall-street-touts-europe-as-winner-in-stock-rally-s-next-leg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街策略师推荐欧洲股市而非美国股市，因为经济前景改善和接近创纪录的折扣推动科技行业以外的股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/wall-street-touts-europe-as-winner-in-stock-rally-s-next-leg</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:50:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维多第二年利润井喷，盈利130亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/vitol-earned-13-billion-in-second-year-of-blowout-profits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，维多集团公布的 2023 年利润约为 130 亿美元，这标志着这家全球最大的独立石油贸易商连续第二年实现丰厚盈利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/vitol-earned-13-billion-in-second-year-of-blowout-profits</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
