      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 08:21:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾暗示如果通胀风险上升将推迟降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/philippines-stands-pat-on-rate-as-inflation-flares-peso-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾央行周一将基准利率维持在17年来的高位，并表示如果通胀风险持续存在，货币宽松政策可能会推迟到明年初。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/philippines-stands-pat-on-rate-as-inflation-flares-peso-weakens</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 07:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在美国关键通胀出现之前，金价攀升至新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/gold-retreats-as-robust-us-data-dampen-rate-cut-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者将注意力转向本周晚些时候关键的美国通胀数据，黄金价格创下每盎司 2,350 美元上方的新纪录，随后回吐涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/gold-retreats-as-robust-us-data-dampen-rate-cut-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 02:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
